title: Ep. - 304 - INES BASIC FROM MARRIED AT FIRST SIGHT AUSTRALIA COFFEY ANDERSON FROM COUNTRY EVER AFTER
description:
Ines Basic, the hilarious star of Married At First Sight Australia, a reality television series in which strangers are paired together by "experts" and unofficially "married. Ines talks about life before she became Australia’s number one reality villain, behind the scenes of the show, the toll it took on her mental health, and her new plans.

 

Country singer Coffey Anderson from Country Ever After on Netflix, which features Coffey and his hip-hop dancer wife, Criscilla, as they juggle family life, career goals and tests of faith.
